OL,3,CBoy aged 15 dies after Donegal
OL,4,CInternational Rally incident
OL,6,FA 15-year-old boy who died after an
OL,7,Fincident at the Donegal International
OL,8,FRally has been named.
OL,10,FTadhg Callaghan Carter died and two
OL,11,Fothers were injured on Saturday, with
OL,12,Fthe remainder of the event cancelled
OL,13,Fas a result.
OL,15,FGardai said that shortly before 5pm
OL,16,Femergency services were alerted after
OL,17,Fa number of onlookers were injured "in
OL,18,Fan incident involving a participating
OL,19,Fcar" at Trentagh, near Kilmacrennan.
OL,26,@wD@FrtyD@dOU{D@DO]
