OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1782139704
OL,3,CBoy aged 15 dies after Donegal
OL,4,CInternational Rally incident
OL,6,FThey said Tadhg was brought by
OL,7,Fambulance from the scene to
OL,8,FLetterkenny University Hospital, where
OL,9,Fhe was later pronounced dead.
OL,11,FTwo other spectators are receiving
OL,12,Fhospital treatment for non-life-
OL,13,Fthreatening injuries.
OL,15,FGardai said the local Coroner has been
OL,16,Fnotified, a post-mortem examination
OL,17,Fwill be arranged and that the road has
OL,18,Fsince reopened.
OL,26,@wD@Frt
