OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1782139704
OL,3,CBoy aged 15 dies after Donegal
OL,4,CInternational Rally incident
OL,6,FThey are appealing for witnesses
OL,7,Fpresent at 'Location 15 on Special
OL,8,FStage 12 Gartan' of the event to
OL,9,Fcontact them.
OL,11,FIn a statement, Motorsport Ireland and
OL,12,FDonegal Motor Club said that "as a
OL,13,Fmark of respect" they have cancelled
OL,14,Fthe remainder of the event.
OL,16,FThey said they were "deeply saddened"
OL,17,Fby what had happened and expressed
OL,18,F"deepest sympathies to the family of
OL,19,Fthe deceased and ask that everyone
OL,20,Frespect their privacy at this time".
OL,26,@tD@^OUuD@PO]xD@UOUxD@eO]zD@AOU|D@cO]
