OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F414A1782139704
OL,3,CBoy aged 15 dies after Donegal
OL,4,CInternational Rally incident
OL,6,FMotorsport Ireland said that as the
OL,7,Fcountry's governing body for four-
OL,8,Fwheeled motorsport, it, along with
OL,9,FGardai, has begun "a full
OL,10,Finvestigation into the circumstances
OL,11,Fof the accident".
OL,13,FBoth the organisation and the Gardai
OL,14,Fsay they are aware video footage of
OL,15,Fthe accident is circulating on social
OL,16,Fmedia and have asked the public not to
OL,17,Fshare it.
OL,19,FThe three-day event bills itself as
OL,20,F"one the toughest rally challenges
OL,21,Fthere is for drivers and teams".
OL,26,@qD@FrtqD@SOUsD@PO]uD@drt|D@AOU}D@_O]
