OL,6,FParticipants compete in 20 stages
OL,7,Faround the north-west coast of the
OL,8,Fcounty.
OL,10,FOrganisers say it attracts more than
OL,11,F70,000 spectators and almost 400,000
OL,12,Fview the rally on TV and online.
